<h4 id="usage-html-js-3"><a href="#usage-html-js-3">HTML structure</a></h4>

<section class="prose">
  <dl>
    <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;button type="button" data-drawer-trigger="{ DRAWER_ID }"&gt;</code></dt>
    <dd>Opens the drawer with the given id.</dd>
    <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;dialog class="drawer" id="{ DRAWER_ID }"&gt;</code></dt>
    <dd>The drawer modal element. It uses <code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code> for native modality and focus handling.</dd>
    <dt><code class="highlight language-html">&lt;button type="button" data-drawer-close&gt;</code></dt>
    <dd>Closes the currently open drawer (use this for close buttons and footer actions).</dd>
  </dl>
</section>

<h4 id="usage-html-js-4"><a href="#usage-html-js-4">Data attributes</a></h4>

<section class="prose">
  <ul>
    <li><code>data-side="bottom|top|left|right"</code> (default <code>bottom</code>).</li>
    <li><code>data-snap-points="0.25,0.5,1"</code>: snap points as fractions (0..1).</li>
    <li><code>data-default-snap="1"</code>: default snap point when opening.</li>
    <li><code>data-handle-only="true|false"</code>: allow dragging only from the handle (default <code>true</code>).</li>
    <li><code>data-close-on-overlay-click="true|false"</code>: close when clicking outside the panel (default <code>true</code>).</li>
    <li><code>data-velocity-threshold="1"</code>: snap velocity threshold (px/ms).</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<h4 id="usage-html-js-5"><a href="#usage-html-js-5">JavaScript events</a></h4>

<section class="prose">
  <dl>
    <dt><code>basecoat:initialized</code></dt>
    <dd>Dispatched on the drawer once it is initialized.</dd>
    <dt><code>basecoat:drawer</code></dt>
    <dd>Dispatched on <code>document</code> when a drawer opens (other drawers listen for this to close).</dd>
    <dt><code>drawer:open</code>, <code>drawer:close</code>, <code>drawer:snap</code></dt>
    <dd>Dispatched on the drawer element for state changes.</dd>
  </dl>
</section>

